Use of information
The information collected through our service will be used for the purposes described in this policy.
For example, we may use your data to:
to operate and improve our service
create game accounts and allow users to play our games
identify and suggest connections to other FFG users
to develop new services
to improve your personal gaming experience
to contact you
Storage duration and deletion
We retain all personal information you provide to us only as long as it is necessary to fulfill the purposes for
    which the information was transmitted, or as required by law.
With fulfillment of the purpose and / or expiry of the legal storage periods, the data will be deleted
    or blocked by us.
Passing on your information
FFG will not disclose your personal information unless you are authorized or as described
    below:
As described above, FFG can work with other companies and individuals to provide services to us.
These agents and service providers may have
    access to your personal information.
We may share information we collect about you with others, such as publishers, business partners, sponsors and advertisers.
We may release your information to the extent permitted by law and share fraud protection information with companies or organizations.
Changes to the policy
We may update this privacy policy and will notify you by email (if you have provided us with your
    personal e-mail address), if we make any relevant changes to the policy.
However, we encourage you to check this page regularly for the latest
    information.
Security
We strive to protect your information from any misuse by storing the information collected in the service in a
    secure environment that is not available to the public.
However, we can not guarantee the absolute security of the transmitted or stored information.
Although we are very concerned about the security of our service, we can not guarantee that third party "hackers" will be prevented from gaining access to your information
    illegally.
Therefore, we provide no guarantee or assurance that your information will be protected from third parties, protected against loss, misuse or
    modification.
We can not do this because no method of transmission or storing over the Internet is completely secure.
Access to personal data and data retention
Contact us at info@funflavorgames.com if you would like us to query, change or delete your personal information from our
    storage. Please note that we need this information to provide our service. We may also retain and use your information as necessary to meet our legal obligations, settle disputes, and enforce our
    agreements.
Age limits of the user
Our games and our websites are not aimed at children under the age of 13. We do not collect information or direct interest-based
    advertising to anyone under the age of 13. If you believe that we have collected information from anyone under the age of 13, please contact us at info@funflavorgames.com. The information will be
    permanently deleted.
